33
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,770
Absolutely not.

34
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,370
Lil' Hammer,

35
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,800
are you actually letting him go?

36
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,760
Remember,

37
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,840
once you step out of Li Fishing Village,

38
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,720
no matter what happens,

39
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,280
you must never speak a word about us.

40
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,360
Lil' Hammer,

41
00:03:27,690 --> 00:03:28,890
you stubborn old man.

42
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,140
