56
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,360
It's said that

57
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,130
the genius sword immortal, Mo Xiao,

58
00:05:27,130 --> 00:05:28,640
is actually the son of the Demon Lord,

59
