76
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:06,520
let alone have a memorial tablet in the Sword Pavilion.

77
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:10,520
It's such a shame to see a great sword immortal

78
00:06:11,410 --> 00:06:13,530
end up like this.

79
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,730
