If he weren't the demon's son,

85
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,760
Luntian Branch wouldn't have

86
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,890
been sealed overnight because of him.

87
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,680
And Master wouldn't have died.

88
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,450
Exactly.

89
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,500
