96
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:52,950
Mo Xiao,

97
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:29,230
for you and for the Shushan Sect,

98
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,060
I cannot take the risk.

99
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,640
Even if I go against the principles of the Shushan Sect

100
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,960
and commit the sin of killing,

101
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,350
I, Yuan Beichen, will bear the consequences alone.

102
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:40,280
Although I've tried countless times to protect you,

103
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:42,150
fate is inescapable.

104
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,230
Life is full of twists and turns.

105
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,420
Mo Xiao,

106
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,690
remember what I've told you.

107
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,920
No matter where you are,

108
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,360
your heart must remain true to the Way.

109
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,360
Mo Xiao.

110
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,000
I want to see him alive,

111
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:19,140
