112
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,200
Sect Leader,

113
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:21,880
bad news!

114
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,400
Mo Xiao is carrying Yuan Beichen's body

115
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:25,860
