116
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:27,960
Mo Xiao,

117
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,760
you are no longer a disciple of the Shushan Sect.

118
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,480
How dare you trespass on Shushan?

119
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,679
According to Shushan's rules,

120
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:34,520
you should be executed on the spot.

121
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:37,320
Yuan Beichen took his own life to atone for his sins at Shushan.

122
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,320
His body cannot be laid to rest in the Sea of Reincarnation,

123
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,480
and his spirit tablet will never be enshrined in the Sword Pavilion.

124
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,880
The Ghost Valley is where traitors belong.

125
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:47,540
Say another word,

126
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:52,560
and I'll kill you all.

127
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:06,760
Mo Xiao,

128
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,210
barging in like this

129
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:12,240
