130
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,960
The Sect Leader of Shushan,

131
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,740
the Branch Leader of Luntian Branch,

132
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:20,640
his body left to rot in Ghost Valley.

133
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:25,020
This is truly the biggest shame for the Luntian Branch.

134
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:10,040
So, you're still alive.

135
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,700
I, Mo Xiao, am guilty.

136
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:16,080
The fault lies entirely with me.

137
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,440
But why must you disgrace my master?

138
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:21,340
Deceiving the Immortal Sect of Shushan,

139
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:23,960
secretly adopting a demon's son,

140
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,730
and eventually succumbing to the Demon Sect.

141
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:29,940
Aren't these crimes

142
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:32,450
enough for him to pay with his life?

143
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,840
Though I am a demon's son,

144
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,760
I've been taught by my master since childhood

145
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:41,520
to protect the immortal sects and safeguard all living beings.

146
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,720
What wrong have I done

147
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:46,100
to deserve my master being humiliated like this by you?

148
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:51,080
Mo Xiao,

149
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:54,120
you were born a demon's son,

150
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:57,040
marked by sin from the start.

151
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,520
This

152
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:00,080
is your fate.

153
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:03,000
As for your master,

154
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:05,090
when he chose to

155
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,210
secretly adopt a demon's son without the immortal sects' knowledge,

156
00:11:08,210 --> 00:11:09,880
he sealed this very outcome.

157
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:10,480
This

158
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,640
is also his fate.

159
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,480
