00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,310
and a descendant of the Nüwa Clan.

558
00:33:17,630 --> 00:33:19,360
As the Chief,

559
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:21,100
I will protect my clan members

560
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:23,330
even if it costs me my life.

561
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:25,520
Fine.

562
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,760
Then you can die.

563
00:34:26,290 --> 00:34:27,350
Murong Changfeng,

564
00:34:27,690 --> 00:34:29,290
we Nüwa are born of divine blood.

565
00:34:29,290 --> 00:34:30,489
We live in seclusion,

566
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:31,040
but you

567
00:34:31,060 --> 00:34:33,320
dare trespass into our Li River and harm my people?

568
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:34,310
Today,

569
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,590
I, Xuyuan Wushuang,

570
00:34:35,679 --> 00:34:36,980
will see to it that you disciples of Shushan

571
00:34:36,980 --> 00:34:38,840
are buried beneath these waters!

572
00:34:52,230 --> 00:34:53,739
So, Mo Xiao,

573
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:57,440
you've truly chosen the path of darkness.

574
00:34:58,450 --> 00:35:00,110
Let's see how far it takes you.

575
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,700
Father.

576
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:12,970
Father.

577
00:35:52,160 --> 00:35:53,000
It's alright.

578
00:35:53,560 --> 00:35:55,090
Everything's alright now.

579
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:57,360
He's only suffered some damage to his spiritual breath.

580
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,820
With a few days of rest, he'll recover fully.

581
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,030
Let's go.

582
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:01,320
Daughter.

583
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,120
Father.

584
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:14,030
Even now,

585
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:17,200
you still don't understand, do you?

586
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:21,540
Back then, your defiance

587
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:23,490
didn't just sever the bond

588
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:26,220
between us.

589
00:37:26,790 --> 00:37:29,190
It wounded the hearts of our people as well.

590
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:33,220
You gave up your role as the Saintess of the Nüwa Clan,

591
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:35,200
and with it,

592
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:38,540
turned away from your duty and responsibility.

593
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:41,400
All for your own desires,

594
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:43,520
you abandoned the clan,

595
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:46,670
and by marrying into

596
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,990
the demon sect,

597
00:37:49,240 --> 00:37:50,900
you brought disgrace upon us.

598
00:37:52,660 --> 00:37:54,960
You didn't just disappoint me.

599
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:58,750
You let down the entire Nüwa Clan.

600
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,820
I know I was wrong, Father.

601
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:04,570
I will repent before

602
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:06,440
the Mother Goddess Nüwa.

603
00:38:09,080 --> 00:38:10,160
Enough.

604
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:13,000
If you still care, even a little,

605
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:15,870
about the future of the Nüwa Clan,

606
00:38:16,310 --> 00:38:17,910
then remember the vow

607
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:20,360
you once made.

608
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:24,970
You are no longer one of us.

609
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:27,280
Don't drag the conflict between the righteous and the demonic

610
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:29,040
back into Li.

611
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:32,840
This is the only way

612
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:35,560
to keep our people safe.

613
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,180
Father,

614
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:38,760
was it because...

615
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,600
Fate plays cruel tricks.

616
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:51,160
Mo Xiao, by some twist of fate,

617
00:38:51,240 --> 00:38:53,480
has ended up on the banks of the Li River.

618
00:38:54,770 --> 00:38:56,660
He is your son.

619
00:38:57,400 --> 00:39:00,400
He also carries the bloodline of our Xuyuan clan.

620
00:39:00,830 --> 00:39:03,150
I couldn't stand by and watch him die,

621
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:09,690
but as you've seen,

622
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:11,150
my choice to save him

623
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:14,560
has drawn disaster upon the Nüwa Clan.

624
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,920
As the Chief,

625
00:39:17,370 --> 00:39:20,260
I can't allow personal sentiment

626
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:23,040
to place our people in jeopardy again.

627
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:31,210
Take him and leave.

628
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,720
Never

629
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:43,350
ever come back again.

630
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:04,080
Father,

631
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:09,800
I understand.

632
00:41:21,100 --> 00:41:22,320
My son,

633
00:41:23,520 --> 00:41:25,080
I've finally found you.

634
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,580
It's you.

635
00:41:46,270 --> 00:41:47,330
Where's the Chief?

636
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,280
Where are the villagers?

637
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,380
They're safe.

638
00:41:49,690 --> 00:41:51,580
Murong Changfeng has already withdrawn.

639
00:41:51,580 --> 00:41:52,960
The fishing village may have been destroyed,

640
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:55,240
but thankfully, the Chief had foreseen this.

641
00:41:55,240 --> 00:41:56,740
He prepared a new settlement in the hills,

642
00:41:56,740 --> 00:41:57,650
moved the tribe there ahead of time,

643
00:41:57,650 --> 00:41:59,510
and safeguarded our foundation.

644
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,520
It's all my fault.
